title: Dragon Scantuary - II
description: Dragon Sanctuary (DS) is a gaming & entertainment ecosystem powered by the BATL SPL utility token. The operation primarily features a series of free-to-play 3D Battle Arena games that merge the thrill of 3D combat with the power of Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs) on the Solana blockchain. In the Dragon Sanctuary, players enter a realm where powerful dragons clash for supremacy in various combat modes. Each dragon character has their own attributes, abilities, & rarity.
